WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.773 --> 00:00:04.728
In accordance with VHA Directive 1761:

2
00:00:04.728 --> 00:00:08.895
Supply Chain Inventory Management, October 24, 2016,

3
00:00:10.609 --> 00:00:13.551
the VISN CLO or designee is responsible

4
00:00:13.551 --> 00:00:16.054
for assessing inventory management programs

5
00:00:16.054 --> 00:00:19.537
at VISN medical facilities through a quality control review

6
00:00:19.537 --> 00:00:21.655
once per fiscal year.

7
00:00:21.655 --> 00:00:25.184
The QCR checklist must be completed at least annually

8
00:00:25.184 --> 00:00:29.202
by the VISN CLO or designee, regardless if the facility

9
00:00:29.202 --> 00:00:32.459
is scheduled for a national OIC review.

10
00:00:32.459 --> 00:00:36.847
Dual campus facilities may complete a combined QCR.

11
00:00:36.847 --> 00:00:41.014
A team from P&amp;LO will join at least one QCR visit per VISN.

12
00:00:42.356 --> 00:00:44.820
The checklist does not exclusively measure

13
00:00:44.820 --> 00:00:46.506
compliance with policy,

14
00:00:46.506 --> 00:00:50.093
but includes questions for informational purposes.

15
00:00:50.093 --> 00:00:51.625
Those questions are designated

16
00:00:51.625 --> 00:00:54.596
with a double asterisk throughout the checklist.

